Class BarComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • komponent.BarComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class BarComponent
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    Main class of bar diagram component. It uses get and set methods to change components properties. Component is a JPanel containing all necessary sub-components to build a bar diagram.
